headline: Acadia Realty Trust (AKR) Q2 FFO Miss Estimates
summary: Acadia Realty Trust (AKR) delivered FFO and revenue surprises of -3.03% and +3.17%, respectively, for the quarter ended June 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?

headline: Federal Realty Investment Trust Recognized Among Top Workplaces Across Three Major Markets
summary: Federal Realty Investment Trust (NYSE:FRT) has again been named one of the best places to work—earning spots on The Washington Post's and The San Francisco Chronicle's 2025 Top Workplaces lists, as well as Philadelphia Business Journal's Best Places to Work in Greater Philadelphia list.
